{"tid":393593,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇巴打絲打夜晚瞓覺會出汗，點搞好","createTime":"2017-09-09T11:18:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-09T11:31:20.000Z","uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4cdeb351af849ae111378766d85cf2aa9ce57d98","tid":393593,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:18:17.000Z","msg":"成日瞓瞓下出汗<br />\n仲要好鬼多<br />\n成個頸背脊濕晒<br />\n床單被鋪枕頭底衫全部都濕晒<br />\n每晚瞓到咁上下就要換衫<br />\n有時仲要沖涼<br />\n明明已經開咗好大冷氣<br />\n而且又唔係覺得好熱<br />\n張被已經唔係太厚<br />\n我可以點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申 之前試過去醫院抽血驗都話無事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464d49a3613ee97d5cb8d52681eeab52363b283b","tid":393593,"uid":28920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:19:36.000Z","msg":"打得j多？"},{"pid":"4e2617fa9911c95981ff4ba6591634975a9e9a38","tid":393593,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:19:40.000Z","msg":"中醫有樣野叫盜汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5735a10c90abf60de36539b2984745a677634ef8","tid":393593,"uid":30966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:20:24.000Z","msg":"有冇發惡夢？"},{"pid":"38b271d53f2d454bcdea9a8e44a77faaccdf824d","tid":393593,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:21:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇發惡夢？</blockquote><br />\n咁又冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n都係一啲奇奇怪怪嘅夢<br />\n但係一啲都唔可怕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9404e9b17255f98927cb891b391b50e07ecef1f8","tid":393593,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":