gmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> plz</blockquote><br />\n有冇夢遺 早洩 捱夜？？"},{"pid":"df103fcc44d759a23aafe5693b63f81b89bf1241","tid":393593,"uid":127116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:26:11.000Z","msg":"我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為只係冷氣唔夠凍<br />\n無諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12b59f4c21babb358fd2225f8bbbc77512e69a9f","tid":393593,"uid":76105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:27:03.000Z","msg":"濕氣太重 去刮沙 拔罐 有幫助 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  或者叫條女幫你抹汗"},{"pid":"d32d2082341088e39ad366656303ad7548d8ce36","tid":393593,"uid":58445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:28:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中醫有樣野叫盜汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肝腎陰虛 想知再講</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> plz</blockquote><br />\n呢d其實唔係咩大事 去睇中醫汁劑藥補補腎就冇事"},{"pid":"bf356d5f48756d4da2ddfac1f1bda138a679a132","tid":393593,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:29:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>中醫有樣野叫盜汗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n肝腎陰虛 想知再講</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> plz</blockquote><br />\n有冇夢遺 早洩 捱夜？？</blockquote><br />\n捱夜有<br />\n不過都係12點左右就訓<br />\n有時九點鐘瞓着一點幾之後出汗<br />\n之後就訓唔番直至到朝頭早"},{"pid":"98309c8646ba017921e68332c409f93d9e6708c8","tid":393593,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:29:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為只係冷氣唔夠凍<br />\n無諗咁多<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/31.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n初頭我都以為係<br />\n之後我較個冷氣最大都係會咁"},{"pid":"094a3d82aa269a4813767129624a21aa80c8761f","tid":393593,"uid":75457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:30:18.000Z","msg":"汗症"},{"pid":"03b5b2aec231c5bfa6a4162bf059fd7da5262d99","tid":393593,"uid":41317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:30:24.000Z","msg":"當歸六黃湯, 飲完個人會即刻出汗, 飲幾日就冇事<br />\n但係好寒, 可能會有少少肚屙"},{"pid":"c687e92253dbd34c2239b575301d4654bb0a3591","tid":393593,"uid":52494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:31:20.000Z","msg":"成日訓教出冷汗搞到訓唔著<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}